window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>With the war almost won, one final confrontation awaits.</b></p> <p>Against all odds, Primal Conjurer Ryn Xaven has beaten back the devil army time and again. Now only one terrifying threat remains: the devil plague. He must ensure it never spreads.</p> <p>After the rescue of an unexpected ally reveals the last of the devil plot, Ryn must act quickly to defeat them. He travels to the Lachlan Confederacy’s capital city of Whitebridge to end the threat.</p> <p>With his powerful and beautiful auxiliaries at his side, Ryn will face down the last of the devil army... and cement his legacy as one of the finest primal conjurers the realm has ever seen.</p>"; 
